---
title: Sri Lankan Potato & Cauliflower Dhal with Garlic Tortilla Chips
description: Put that take-away flyer down because we've got something in store for you. Sri Lankan spices work their magic with hearty lentils and creamy coconut milk in our new favourite dhal recipe. Oven-baked tortilla chips work a treat for scooping up the deliciousness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/657a3d82a65f6d71569fbef8-9e989ffc.jpeg
